ActSeeds Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Seeds Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the SEEDS REGULATIONS in order to (1) reduce regulatory burden on developers of new oilseed soybean and forage crop varieties and facilitate market entry; and (2) remove the confusion between suspension and cancellation of variety registration, as recommended by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
